text.tspan: Can you imagine life without portable communication
devices? Living without your laptop, tablet or mobile
phone? However, none of these useful and entertaining
devices are of any use to us if the battery is empty. So,
chargers are one of those tiny things of great importance.
We expect them to be fast charging, reliable, convenient
and green. Modern chargers especially designed with the
USB standard offer all of these aspects - with the help of
Infineon’s semiconductors, first and foremost gallium
nitride components, reduce energy losses and increase
performance. They also promote USB-C technology,
which helps avoid large amounts of electronic waste.
